{"tid":844942,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"每逢上體育堂對毒撚黎講永遠都係最大嘅屈辱...","createTime":"2018-10-02T09:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T15:32:39.000Z","uid":71508,"like":43,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b5a4a58d79aec30675c4e21a4cfaec285c7c3c3b","tid":844942,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:17:39.000Z","msg":"毒撚又冇自信 體育又差 <br />\n永遠打羽毛球,乒乓波被mk㩒住黎打 <br />\n推鉛球擲鐵餅扔標槍次次都係最近嗰個 <br />\n跑步跑最慢 圍圈跑其實已經跑到想死 但為面子死都繼續堅持 <br />\n划艇成績全班最差 <br />\n團體比賽仲慘 打籃球排球足球永遠都企喺角落 唔知做咩好 柒到想搵窿捐 人地打波流下嘅係汗水 我地被波打所流下嘅係淚水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lm <br />\n體育堂,永遠都係毒撚永遠的痛 <br />\n永遠都係毒撚嘅屈辱 即使公開試考得幾好 望住班成績垃圾但因識運動而晚晚有低form妹幫佢抹汗 含拎 比個豬佢食 <br />\n係你日後即使有幾咁成功 都係個無法彌補嘅痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lm"},{"pid":"d0f589147da23728ab27015077256f8b9adbcad3","tid":844942,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f00d9118916de1ad38fd17ecc940b1615705a68","tid":844942,"uid":146063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:47:01.000Z","msg":"坐係長櫈圍爐 一齊望住其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ecd13c12426760e0da22cbab8f723596cb7040","tid":844942,"uid":116364,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T11:49:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c9e13ad4ead56b0a1f67644eb4509de86551b42","tid":844942,"uid":116364,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T11:55:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"667817aeaa7634fce2d6a145b6f2961baf20b